{"tid":2021899,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疑新冠肺炎併發川崎病亡 英男嬰死前兩小時仍面露笑容","createTime":"2020-05-18T04:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T04:32:46.000Z","uid":225130,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"58afc5ae9ef582abfba37aaab798a9f13af1446b","tid":2021899,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T04:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.singtao.ca/wp-content/uploads/master_sandbox/2020/05/2020051715563375028.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.singtao.ca%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fmaster_sandbox%2F2020%2F05%2F2020051715563375028.jpg&h=7db04627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n意大利、西班牙和英國發現多名兒童，身體出現原因未明的神秘嚴重炎症，部分患者送院時發高燒和動脈腫脹，疑似患上嚴重川崎症，甚至有兒童因此死亡。英國一名8個月大的男嬰，上月初確診感染新冠肺炎，其後病情惡化。上月底懷疑因新冠病毒併發川崎病死亡，相信為同類個案的最年輕死者。<br />\n<br />\n男嬰亞歷山大（Alexander Parsons）原本並無其他疾病，但在上月6日開始，出現如曬傷的出疹、發高燒，以及淋巴腫大。其後，其手及腳掌亦變紅。母親羅蘭茲（Kathryn Rowlands）當時以為他感染病毒，隨即致電報警，對方則估計他患上腮腺炎。其後，亞歷山大病情惡化，被送往一間兒童醫院接受治療，翌日確診川崎病。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n經心臟掃瞄後發現，他有多個冠狀動脈瘤、動脈異常擴大及積水，最終於上月25日離世。在其死前2小時拍攝的照片顯示，亞歷山大當時仍面露笑容，但其後卻因動脈瘤破裂而離世。在防疫措施下，父母之中只能有其中一人陪伴亞歷山大，因此父親喬恩（Jon）未能見兒子最後一面。<br />\n<br />\n羅蘭茲與喬恩正等候驗屍結果。羅蘭茲指，無法想像自己懷胎的時間比亞歷山大的生存時間更長，並指「我生命再也不完整了」。她又指，希望政府聽取科學家意見，研究新冠病毒與川崎病的的關係，並呼籲政府不要再將生命作賭注。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n----<br />\n<br />\n仆街支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"000ef46d94400f3ec5911c0c7a45998cc6dc872a","tid":2021899,"uid":41873,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T04:26:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">武漢肺炎</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4394e34b362854cfa65dec0ebde3878cb2694330","tid":2021899,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T04:26:55.000Z","msg":"川崎氏症並不常見[1]，每10萬名5歲以下人口中，僅會出現8至67位患者；但在日本，每10萬人中就有124位患者[4]。患者幾乎都在五歲以內[1]；男孩較女孩容易罹患此症[1]。西元1967年，日本小兒科醫師川崎富作率先提報此病，故依此命名為川崎氏病[4][5]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解人地無玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3699e2976e5c8d72fe0aa34d4096f95efbd86d9","tid":2021899,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T04:28:07.000Z","msg":"要不是中國人周圍播毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1e491ec728cbf6ba709c177eefa3e660a488ce","tid":2021899,"uid":4840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T04:28:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那"},{"pid":"52387c35176b56342ba3f1ab7f463a7c720a1bfb","tid":2021899,"uid":28547,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T04:30:39.000Z","msg":"什麼川崎病？為什麼要傷害日本人民的感情？"},{"pid":"d382e8884ee7bc13c27a81b85aacb1f79da93e14","tid":2021899,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4394e34b362854cfa65dec0ebde3878cb2694330","tid":2021899,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T04:26:55.000Z","msg":"川崎氏症並不常見[1]，每10萬名5歲以下人口中，僅會出現8至67位患者；但在日本，每10萬人中就有124位患者[4]。患者幾乎都在五歲以內[1]；男孩較女孩容易罹患此症[1]。西元1967年，日本小兒科醫師川崎富作率先提報此病，故依此命名為川崎氏病[4][5]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解人地無玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0